<p>I have two rows in  my table as shown in this jsfiddle link, <a href="http://jsfiddle.net/o6ew3zom/" rel="nofollow">http://jsfiddle.net/o6ew3zom/</a>.</p>  <p>I select all rows using <code>table tr</code> and access the next row as,</p>  <pre><code>$(this).next() </code></pre>  <p>It prints, </p>  <pre><code>the current element id is  firstRow the next element id is undefined the current element id is  secondRow the next element id is undefined </code></pre>  <p>I expect,</p>  <pre><code>    the current element id is  firstRow     the next element id is secondRow     the current element id is  secondRow     the next element id is undefined </code></pre>